@startuml
title Autopatzer System - Deployment and Connectivity Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "React UI\n(Electron App)" as UI
participant "WebSocket\n(autopatzerd)" as WS
participant "Lichess API\n(Event Stream)" as Lichess
participant "Perl\nCommunication Layer" as Perl
participant "Teensy 3.2\nMicrocontroller" as Teensy
participant "A4988\nStepper Drivers" as Drivers
participant "NEMA17\nMotors (X/Y)" as Motors
participant "CD4051B\nMultiplexers" as Mux
participant "Hall Effect\nSensors" as Sensors
participant "IRF540N MOSFET\n(Electromagnet)" as Magnet

== System Initialization and Network Setup ==

User -> UI: Launch Application
activate UI
UI -> UI: Fetch Current IP Address\n(useEffect/useInterval)
UI -> Lichess: Establish WebSocket Connection\n(useLichessEventStream)
activate Lichess
Lichess --> UI: Connection Established
UI -> WS: Establish WebSocket Connection\n(useBoardEventStream)
activate WS
WS --> UI: Connection Established
UI -> Teensy: Initialize via Perl Layer
activate Perl
Perl -> Teensy: Send Initialization Commands
activate Teensy
Teensy -> Drivers: Initialize Stepper Drivers
activate Drivers
Teensy -> Mux: Configure Multiplexer Channels
activate Mux
Teensy --> Perl: Initialization Complete
Perl --> UI: System Ready
UI --> User: Display Home Screen

== Game Start and Connectivity ==

User -> UI: Select Game/Start Match
UI -> Lichess: Request Game Stream\n(Lichess Boards API)
Lichess --> UI: Game Data & Stream Events
UI -> WS: Subscribe to Board Events
WS --> UI: Board Event Stream Active

== Move Detection and Processing ==

Lichess -> UI: Opponent Move Event\n(WebSocket)
UI -> UI: Update Game State\n(React Component)
UI -> WS: Send Move Command
WS -> Perl: Relay Move Instructions
Perl -> Teensy: Transmit Move Coordinates
Teensy -> Drivers: Calculate Motor Steps\n(AccelStepper)
Drivers -> Motors: Drive X-Axis Motor
activate Motors
Motors --> Drivers: Position Reached
Drivers -> Motors: Drive Y-Axis Motor
Motors --> Drivers: Position Reached
deactivate Motors
Teensy -> Magnet: Activate Electromagnet\n(via MOSFET)
activate Magnet
Magnet --> Teensy: Piece Grabbed
Teensy -> Drivers: Move to Target Position
activate Motors
Drivers -> Motors: Execute Movement
Motors --> Drivers: Target Reached
deactivate Motors
Teensy -> Magnet: Deactivate Electromagnet
deactivate Magnet
Teensy -> Mux: Select Sensor Channel
Mux -> Sensors: Read Hall Effect Values
activate Sensors
Sensors --> Mux: Analog Signal
deactivate Sensors
Mux --> Teensy: Sensor Reading
Teensy -> Perl: Position Confirmed
Perl -> WS: Board State Update
WS -> UI: Update Board Display
UI --> User: Show Updated Position

== User Move Execution ==

User -> UI: Make Physical Move
UI -> Teensy: Monitor Board via Perl
Teensy -> Mux: Scan All Sensor Positions
loop For Each Board Square
    Mux -> Sensors: Read Position
    activate Sensors
    Sensors --> Mux: Piece Presence
    deactivate Sensors
    Mux --> Teensy: Sensor Data
end
Teensy -> Perl: Detected Board Changes
Perl -> WS: Move Detected
WS -> UI: Board Change Event
UI -> UI: Validate Move\n(ConfirmMove Component)
UI --> User: Display Move Confirmation
User -> UI: Confirm Move
UI -> Lichess: Send Move via API\n(POST Request)
Lichess --> UI: Move Accepted
UI -> WS: Update Local Board State
UI --> User: Display Move Confirmation\n(Moves Component)

== Continuous Connectivity Monitoring ==

loop During Active Game
    Lichess -> UI: Heartbeat/Keep-Alive
    UI --> Lichess: Acknowledge
    WS -> UI: Board Status Updates
    UI --> WS: Acknowledge
    UI -> Teensy: Poll Sensors via Perl
    Teensy -> Mux: Multiplex Sensor Inputs
    Mux -> Sensors: Read All Positions
    activate Sensors
    Sensors --> Mux: Analog Readings
    deactivate Sensors
    Mux --> Teensy: Consolidated Data
    Teensy --> Perl: Board State
    Perl --> WS: State Update
    WS --> UI: Real-time Board Status
end

== Game Completion ==

Lichess -> UI: Game Over Event
UI -> UI: Display Result\n(Result Component)
UI --> User: Show Game Outcome
UI -> Teensy: Reset Board via Perl
Teensy -> Drivers: Return to Home Position
activate Motors
Drivers -> Motors: Execute Homing Sequence
Motors --> Drivers: Home Position Reached
deactivate Motors
deactivate Drivers
deactivate Mux
Teensy --> Perl: Board Reset Complete
Perl --> WS: Ready for New Game
WS --> UI: System Ready
deactivate Teensy
deactivate Perl
deactivate WS
deactivate Lichess
UI --> User: Return to Home Screen
deactivate UI

@enduml
